arr.some(fn)     → true if AT LEAST ONE element satisfies fn
arr.every(fn)    → true if ALL elements satisfy fn
arr.sort(fn)     → sorts IN PLACE (modifies original!)
arr.flat()       → flattens nested arrays one level
